Slightly wide outside the off stump, Prince slashes and edges it hard to right of Younis, the lone slipper, who lunges across to take a smart catch.

dismissalComment.html: That's it ...  Pakistan wrap up  comprehensive series-levelling win. Great comeback win from them. Victory by 141 runs. Akmal, who has been under the kosh, brings up the victory with a smart stumping. Malik slips it down the leg side, Pollock overbalances himself while trying to flick it and is dragged out of the crease. He can only get back his feet on the line before Akmal knocks the bails off.

dismissalComment.html: All in due time but first he gets rid of Gibbs. All the same an Asif special, pitched close to the off stump line and nipping back in. Up goes the finger and that's a priceless wicket

dismissalText.commentary: Ashwell Prince c Younis Khan b Azhar Mahmood 2 (4b 0x4 0x6 12m) SR: 50

dismissalComment.html: Redemption song for Mahmood. It took two years for him to come back into the team. He played for the county, for the domestic team and generally wallowed outside the team. But what a dramatic comeback, helped by Prince. Strikes gold with his first ball. Slightly wide outside the off stump, Prince slashes and edges it hard to right of Younis, the lone slipper, who lunges across to take a smart catch.

dismissalText.long: st Kamran Akmal b Shoaib Malik
dismissalText.commentary: Shaun Pollock st Kamran Akmal b Shoaib Malik 32 (34b 3x4 1x6 51m) SR: 94.11

dismissalComment.html: That's it ...  Pakistan wrap up  comprehensive series-levelling win. Great comeback win from them. Victory by 141 runs. Akmal, who has been under the kosh, brings up the victory with a smart stumping. Malik slips it down the leg side, Pollock overbalances himself while trying to flick it and is dragged out of the crease. He can only get back his feet on the line before Akmal knocks the bails off.
